.container(style="padding-top: 10px")
    .row
        .row.well
            .col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2
                h1.text-center One click class setup
                    .form-horizontal(role="form")
                p No need to fill in full registration just yet, but please do enter a real email address and a class name so we can send you secure access to your class progress dashboard. 
                .form-group
                    .col-sm-3
                        label.control-label Email
                    .col-sm-9
                        input.form-control#email(type="text", ng-model="signup.emailAddress", on-enter="signup.focusClassCode();")
                        br

                    .col-xs-12
                        center
                            button.btn.btn-primary(ng-click="signup.register();", ng-disabled="signup.canSubmit()") Try it out
                        br
